Connect to DISPLAY (default: :0)
.TP
.BR -D, --debug
Print debugging messages
.TP
.BR \-h, \-\-help
Show this help and exit
.TP
.BR \-V, \-\-version
Show version info and exit

.SS MODIFIER
.TP
.BR \-r, \-\-reload
Reload subtle
.TP
.BR \-q, \-\-quit
Quit subtle
.TP
.BR \-C, \-\-current
Select current active window/view
.TP
.BR \-X, \-\-select
Select a window via pointer

